BUILD DEPENDENCIES: EPICS_BASE
PROCEDURE:
- Copied <top>/Makefile and <top>/config from xxx.
- Extracted stdApp.tar into std1-1.
- Deleted manual version control copies and Unix links; i.e., SGM_1.7a,
	saveData_1.7.c, etc..
- Modifications to stdApp/Db;
	- Deleted unsupported and/or outdated files:
		- table_5.1x
		- table_5.1x.db
	- Removed "DB += scanParms.template" from Makefile.Host;
	scanParms.template link deleted.
	
- Modifications to stdApp/op/adl;
	- Deleted unsupported, outdated or duplicate files:
		- xxx.adl
		- kohzu2SeqCtl_tiny.adl
		- xx_ID_taper_ctrl_1.0.adl
		- BMBPM_old.adl
		- IDBPM_old.adl
