	- Moved the following top-level user displays from stdApp/op/adl to
	xxx/xxxApp/op/adl.
		- 1bma_beamline.adl	
		- 3idd.adl
		- bcda2.adl
		- 2ided_beamline.adl
- Modifications to stdApp/src;
	- Deleted unsupported, outdated or duplicate files:
		- sscanRecord_5.1.dbd
		- devVXStats.c (use base version)
		- devSerial.cc
	- Change "SHARE_BIN = ." to "STD_BIN = ." in Makefile.Vx.
	- Delete "USER_DBDFLAGS += -I .. -I $(EPICS_BASE)/dbd" and
		"PROD += caExample" from Makefile.Host.
	- Remove vxWorks installation from Makefile.Vx.  EPICS compatible
	vxWorks kernel won't be built in VX_CONFIG_DIR.  Copy vxWorks and
	vxWorks.sym into xxx/bin/<Target_Arch> before creating distribution
	tar ball.
	- stdLIBOBJS; change all occurences of $(SHARE_BIN) to $(STD_BIN).
- Configured <top>/config/RELEASE.


